OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784126890
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from their homes
OL,4,Cafter fire breaks out near London rail
OL,5,Cline
OL,7,FDozens of people were evacuated from
OL,8,Ftheir homes in east London after fire
OL,9,Fbroke out near a railway line.
OL,11,FMore than 100 firefighters were called
OL,12,Fto a residential street in Walthamstow
OL,13,Fwhere one house was badly damaged by
OL,14,Ffire and a number of gardens and sheds
OL,15,Falso affected.
OL,17,FSpecial centres were set up for
OL,18,Fevacuated residents after what the
OL,19,FLondon Fire Brigade described as a
OL,20,F"significant incident".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
