PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784126890
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from their homes
OL,4,Cafter fire breaks out near London rail
OL,5,Cline
OL,7,FOne resident, Rebecca Verde told ITV
OL,8,FNews London: "Last night at about
OL,9,F6:30pm I could hear a lot of sirens
OL,10,Fand smell smoke in my flat.
OL,12,F"My husband ran out after seeing where
OL,13,Fthe smoke was coming from and he told
OL,14,Fme to get the kids and get out.
OL,16,F"So I grabbed the kids and the dog
OL,17,Fjust a police were cordoning it off
OL,18,Fand they were going in to evacuate the
OL,19,Fbuilding.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784126890
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from their homes
OL,4,Cafter fire breaks out near London rail
OL,5,Cline
OL,7,F"The fire was big and stretched all
OL,8,Fthe way back behind us and down the
OL,9,Froad.
OL,11,F"We were allowed back in the house
OL,12,Flast night after they got it under
OL,13,Fcontrol."
OL,15,FThe fire brigade said a second home
OL,16,Fnear Vallentin Road and Shernhall
OL,17,FStreet was also partly damaged by the
OL,18,Ffire and thirty gardens were affected,
OL,19,Fadding: "A railway embankment was also
OL,20,Falight and this has caused disruption
OL,21,Fto the Weaver London Overground line.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
