PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1784126890
OL,3,CDozens evacuated from their homes
OL,4,Cafter fire breaks out near London rail
OL,5,Cline
OL,7,F"We have worked closely with Transport
OL,8,Ffor London and the British Transport
OL,9,FPolice to support passengers on
OL,10,Fstopped trains. All passengers have
OL,11,Fnow left the railway."
OL,13,FA number of gas cylinders also had to
OL,14,Fbe cooled down to reduce the risk of
OL,15,Fan explosion. The fire was under
OL,16,Fcontrol just after 10:30pm.
OL,18,FThe cause of the fire is being
OL,19,Finvestigated.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
